title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 22 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 22 2022
description:
Crime, immigration and the economy are the keys to a GOP midterm victory. Buck says, "'Economy, the border, crime.' I'm going to sleep at night muttering this to myself. That's how focused in we are on this." Polls breaking in favor of Republicans. If your family's safety matters, the midterms matter. Clay describes how he talked with his wife for the first time ever about where it's safe for her to buy gas. C&B go through the very latest midterm polling data. 18-year-old murdered by leftist in N. Dakota in what police say was a "politically motivated" crime. The suspect was released on bail, charged only with vehicular homicide. Did Biden's Palpatine speech inspire this insane leftist? Fox report on what it's like to run a small business in lawless Los Angeles. The Red Wave is building.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
